    <string name="about_title">About</string>
    <string name="about_livingroom">Author: Chase Thorne\nVersion: 1.0\n\nInstructions:</string>
    <string name="about_television">\tTelevision Controls:
        \n\- Power on or off the TV with the top-left button.
        \n\- Navigate the menus with the arrow buttons.
        \n\- Select a menu item with the Enter button, located in the center of the arrows
        \n\- Enter the desired channel in the text box below the arrows.
        \n\- The back button, located to the bottom left, returns you to your previous page or channel.
        \n\- The microphone prompts you to speak aloud the desired channel to go to, rather than typing it in the text box.</string>
    <string name="about_lights">\tLight Controls:
        \n\- Move the sliders to control the lights.
        \n\- Left to dim or shut off, right to brighten or turn on.
        \n\- Click the \"CHOOSE COLOR\" button to change the light\'s color.</string>
    <string name="about_blinds">\tBlinds Controls:
        \n\- Move the sliders control the blinds.
        \n\- Left to lower, right to raise.</string>
    <string name="about_credits">\tCredits:
        \nBlinds icons from Icons8 @ https://icons8.com</string>
